article.description: — Alex Hunter had 20 points as Furman romped past The Citadel 94-59 on Saturday.
article.headline: Hunter scores 20 to lift Furman over The Citadel 94-59
article.linkText: Hunter scores 20 to lift Furman over The Citadel 94-59
article.story: CHARLESTON, S.C. -- — Alex Hunter had 20 points as Furman romped past The Citadel 94-59 on Saturday. Mike Bothwell had 17 points for Furman (20-11, 12-6 Southern Conference). Marcus Foster added 15 points. Tyrese Hughey had 10 points and seven rebounds. Hayden Brown had 17 points and 18 rebounds for the Bulldogs (12-17, 6-12). Tyler Moffe added 11 points. David Maynard had 10 points. The Paladins improve to 2-0 against the Bulldogs for the season. Furman defeated The Citadel 102-83 on Feb. 2. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
